<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
The high appetite due to regeneration is annoying, but can be balanced with slow digestion (zombie, etc). Using the racial power can keep you from dying from starvation for a while, before you find a corpse to eat. (use the 'n' to eat all once you started). <p>
There is one mage class that Troll Zombies should try: alchemist. Low INT and WIS is irrelevant. In version 2.2.7 and up, even the wand fail rates aren't affected... 
</p>
<p>
Zombie trolls have the max possible hit dice of 15, and regenerate to boot. That's the ultimate melee, good for alchemists and unbelievers. 
</p>
